RestTemplate to Load balanced RestTemplate

after setting up eureka clients and server if we make http call using client service name as
instead of
Company company = restTemplate.getForObject("http://localhost:8081/companies/"+job.getCompanyId(),Company.class);
to
Company company = restTemplate.getForObject("http://COMPANYMS/companies/"+job.getCompanyId(),Company.class);

will not work as we are using normal version of restTemple not a Load Balanced one
so AppConfig class provides that required LoadBalanced version of RestTemplate